headline: Starbucks (NasdaqGS:SBUX) Partners with GFN for Global Hunger Relief Expansion
summary: Starbucks (NasdaqGS:SBUX) recently announced a partnership with the Global FoodBanking Network to improve food security, making strides in corporate social responsibility. Despite broader market pressures, which saw indices like the S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite experience declines of 6% and 8% respectively due to tariff concerns and a weak U.S. economy outlook, Starbucks managed a 7% price increase over the last quarter. This increase comes amid its ongoing commitment to food rescue...
